{"tid":2093752,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"世衞突然更改紀錄 駐華辦公室先通報病例而非中國政府","createTime":"2020-07-04T05:25:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T11:23:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":600,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":121,"replies":[{"pid":"f4a471335a57ba20ff8293146dcc5103a908dbe5","tid":2093752,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T05:25:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200704/J2XZFU5MNM53MMJL343URLQD6E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200704%2FJ2XZFU5MNM53MMJL343URLQD6E%2F&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IPMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=cbb2509b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200704%2FJ2XZFU5MNM53MMJL343URLQD6E%2F&h=37276caa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200704/J2XZFU5MNM53MMJL343URLQD6E/</a><br />\n<br />\n世界衞生組織更新官網上有關武漢肺炎疫情的時序紀錄，顯示世衞去年底首次接到武漢爆發肺炎病毒的警告，是由世衞駐華代表處發出，而非中國政府主動向世衞通報示警。"},{"pid":"d93712f6a44d1899cc37f931823bb7d2ce5982e8","tid":2093752,"uid":214502,"like":273,"dislike":2,"score":271,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T05:25:38.000Z","msg":"二五狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c675995f3cab8fc552ff4e1992320950cd85291","tid":2093752,"uid":219010,"like":235,"dislike":3,"score":232,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T05:25:46.000Z","msg":"開始轉口風<br />\n<br />\n唔好縮啊"},{"pid":"127f3e25f936823066b628ae4d26a62e9c9ecf50","tid":2093752,"uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d93712f6a44d1899cc37f931823bb7d2ce5982e8","tid":2093752,"uid":214502,"like":273,"dislike":2,"score":271,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T05:25:38.000Z","msg":"二五狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T05:26:18.000Z","